import React from "react"

import Header from "libs/components/molecules/Header"
import { Route, Router, Routes } from "react-router-dom"
import Main from "libs/components/views/ain"

function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Header />
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<Main />} />
      </Routes>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
